response.overview: Enraged and thirsty for vengeance, a mob of torch-bearing villagers march through an Erie wood in search of an evil child eating woman. But dealing their own brand of Justice might be the worst mistake of their lives, as the one they seek possesses a darker power than they would have ever imagined. Spider Woman: Death's Web spends the nightmarish tale of an unsuspecting group of people encountering a mystical world of buried secrets, human possession and gigantic spiders. Evil never takes kindly to those who oppose it... And in this case, it's counter tech pounces with eight legged agility!
response.title: Spider Woman: Death's Web
